original_title: アンアフェア　－婦人警官の出番、再び!!－
overview: A few days after the last incident, many of the Emmanet-related backroom organizations were arrested. But the turmoil was just the beginning of a new affair... Director Mikio Hirota, who worked on "Shin Megami Tensei", presents crime entertainment with Anri Suzuki, who is at the peak of popularity, as the star.
title: Unaffair - The Officer Comes Again!!
